pull_request.title: Bump oqs-sys/liboqs from `af1b14e` to `352b5d3`
pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `af1b14e` to `352b5d3`.
Commits
  • 352b5d3 Bump PQClean commit number in copy_from_upstream.yml
  • ac2b828 Pull latest verison of McEliece from PQClean
  • 72dfa5a Add Wno-language-extension-token for McEliece/avx
  • 5572f76 Upstream patch to remove __m256i_u* casts from McEliece/avx
  • d682661 Remove unused McEliece implementations
  • 9b77b33 Revert local McEliece changes
  • 3a4ef54 copy_from_upstream: patch mechanism (#944)
  • 4b1a9e2 Make OQS_USE_CPU_EXTENSIONS imply OQS_PORTABLE_BUILD=OFF; alternative to #939...
  • e116748 these two example files got moved at some time (#938)
  • 707750e Fix OQS_PORTABLE_BUILD logic for Frodo (#927)
  • Additional commits viewable in compare view
